OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThere will
OL,6,Fbe a little brightness at first,
OL,7,Fotherwise a cloudy evening with some
OL,8,Flight and patchy rain. Becoming dry
OL,9,Fwith clear spells over Shetland
OL,10,Fovernight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FDry and bright start for
OL,13,FShetland, otherwise a mostly cloudy
OL,14,Fday with patchy rain. Some haar at
OL,15,Ftimes over Shetland.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FSome
OL,18,Frain on Monday morning then becoming
OL,19,Fdry and bright. Breezy with sunshine
OL,20,Fand a few showers on Tuesday. Mostly
OL,21,Fsunny with light winds on Wednesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
